    </a><a href="#howsoonshouldyousendacandidaterejectionletter" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">2. How Soon Should You Send A Candidate Rejection Letter?
    </a><a href="#whatlegalityshouldyouworryaboutwhensendingoutajobrejectionletter" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">3. What Legality Should You Worry About When Sending Out A Job Rejection Letter?
